{"id": 1329, "title": "Ticket #1329: private network settings ignored in file transfer", "description": "<blockquote>\nThe file transfer object directly calls Sock::connect() rather than going through daemon client.  For better or worse, daemon client is where all the private network logic is, so this means that file transfer connections ignore private network settings.\n\n<p>This is a problem for a dual homed submit node that can only be reached by some execute nodes via a private network.  We ran into this in the UW Coon Chemistry lab.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2010-Apr-09 12:08</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/601e174ae640b56c23e1875a20b0832b075f104b\">[25427]</a></span>: Documented fix for file transfer ignoring private network settings. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1329\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1329'); return false;\" title=\"private network settings ignored in file transfer\">#1329</a></span>  (By Dan Bradley )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2010-Apr-05 12:37</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/9102eeb10092c0c13ad58d766c089759a3213c28\">[17780]</a></span>: Added test of CCB in private network. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1329\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1329'); return false;\" title=\"private network settings ignored in file transfer\">#1329</a></span> Confirms that all connections bypass CCB when private network name matches.  (By Dan Bradley )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2010-Apr-05 12:07</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/02b8d29ba3f1e8f2cedcb5a20df5e5da292ac210\">[17779]</a></span>: File transfer was not using private network settings. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1329\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1329'); return false;\" title=\"private network settings ignored in file transfer\">#1329</a></span>  (By Dan Bradley )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "defect", "last_change": "2010-Apr-05 12:38", "status": "resolved", "created": "2010-Apr-05 11:50", "fixed_version": "2010-Apr-05 11:50", "broken_version": "v070400", "priority": "4", "subsystem": "", "assigned_to": "danb", "derived_from": "", "creator": "danb", "rust": "", "customer_group": "other", "visibility": "public", "notify": "dan@hep.wisc.edu", "due_date": ""}